 IIF (SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,2,1)='/' AND SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,5,1)='/', TO_DATE('0' || question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created, 'MM/DD/YYYY'),
  IIF (SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,3,1)='/' AND SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,5,1)='/', TO_DATE(SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,1,3) || '0' || SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,4,6), 'MM/DD/YYYY'),
   IIF (SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,2,1)='/' AND SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,4,1)='/', TO_DATE('0' || SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,1,2) || '0' || SUBSTR(question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_datetime_created,3,6), 'MM/DD/YYYY'),NULL))))

attributes.name: Max Errors Per Batch Upload Insert
Truncate Target Table Before Data Upload
WaitTime In Seconds For S3 File Consistency

object.customQuery:
SELECT bls.batch_id
  FROM metal.batch_load_summary bls
 WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'ADM'
   AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
   AND bls.batch_id = (
       SELECT MAX(batch_id)
         FROM metal.batch_load_summary
        WHERE source_system_code = 'ADM'
          AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
       )
